Sri Lanka diesel , jet tender awarded to BB Energy . Sri Lanka ' s state - owned Ceylon Petroleum Corp ( CPC ) has bought by tender 160 , 000 barrels of gas oil and 40 , 000 barrels of jet fuel from BB Energy for December 19 - 20 delivery , a CPC source said on Friday . The 1 . 0 - percent sulphur gas oil and jet A - 1 were both purchased at a premium of $ 0 . 98 per barrel to Singapore spot quotes , on a cost - and - freight basis to Colombo . The tender closed on November 27 and were valid until November 28 . In its last tender , which was awarded to Dutch trader Vitol , Sri Lanka bought 120 , 000 barrels of gas oil and 80 , 000 barrels of jet fuel at a premium of 67 . 5 cents and 47 . 5 cents , respectively , both over Singapore spot quotes on a c - and - f basis for December 12 - 13 delivery . - - Singapore Newsroom ( + 65 - 870 - 3093 ) 
